name: Think Fast
description:
In this game you have to think fast in order to complete the levels. there are all together 24 challenging levels in which you need to swerve around corners without touching them.

the controls are the arrow keys and at any time you can just press escape and skip a level if it is too hard. you select levels by clicking on them.

i challenge you to finish all of these levels in less than 30 minutes.

Oh and one last thing, i am not responsible for any damage due to rage this game causes. Have fun.

(to start playing just click on the coloured boxes)
